es.ull.isaatc.simulation.parallel
Class SimulationObject

java.lang.Object
  es.ull.isaatc.simulation.parallel.SimulationObject
All Implemented Interfaces:
Identifiable, SimulationObject, java.lang.Comparable<SimulationObject>
Direct Known Subclasses:
BasicFlow, VariableStoreSimulationObject
public abstract class SimulationObject
extends java.lang.Object
implements SimulationObject

An identifiable object belonging to a simulation which can be compared. The identifier is unique per type of simulation object, thus different types of simulation objects can use the same identifiers.

Author:
Iván Castilla Rodríguez
